"block text-black dark:text-white hover:bg-sky-600 dark:hover:bg-sky-800 px-3 py-2 rounded bg-sky-600 dark:bg-sky-800 font-semibold" href="https://pokesymbols.com/tcg">TCG</a><div class="mt-1 pl-2 border-l-2 border-sky-200 text-black dark:text-white"><a class="block w-full text-left pl-5 pr-4 py-2 border-l-2 border-transparent text-black hover:bg-sky-900/20 dark:text-white  dark:hover:bg-sky-800 hover:text-black dark:hover:text-white bg-sky-900/20 font-semibold border-sky-500" href="https://pokesymbols.com/tcg/sets">Sets</a><a class="block w-full text-left pl-5 pr-4 py-2 border-l-2 border-transparent text-black hover:bg-sky-900/20 dark:text-white  dark:hover:bg-sky-800 hover:text-black dark:hover:text-white" href="https://pokesymbols.com/tcg/japanese-sets">Japanese Sets</a><a class="block w-full text-left pl-5 pr-4 py-2 border-l-2 border-transparent text-black hover:bg-sky-900/20 dark:text-white  dark:hover:bg-sky-800 hover:text-black dark:hover:text-white" href="https://pokesymbols.com/tcg/booster-pack-art">Booster Pack Art</a><a class="block w-full text-left pl-5 pr-4 py-2 border-l-2 border-transparent text-black hover:bg-sky-900/20 dark:text-white  dark:hover:bg-sky-800 hover:text-black dark:hover:text-white" href="https://pokesymbols.com/tcg/rarities">Rarities</a></div></div><a class="block text-black dark:text-white hover:bg-sky-600 dark:hover:bg-sky-800 px-3 py-2 rounded" href="https://pokesymbols.com/about">About</a></div></nav><main><div id="raptive-leaderboard-target" class="min-h-[50px] md:min-h-[90px] lg:min-h-[90px]"></div><div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-md p-4 md:p-6 max-w-2xl sm:mx-auto m-6 mb-24"><div class="relative w-full h-auto rounded-lg bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 p-4 sm:min-h-[340px] flex items-center"><div class="relative w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center"><picture class="backface-hidden block"><source srcset="/images/tcg/sets/symbols/mega-evolution.avif" type="image/avif"><img src="./Mega_Evolution_files/mega-evolution.png" alt="Set Symbol"></picture><picture class="backface-hidden hidden"><source srcset="/images/tcg/sets/logos/mega-evolution.avif" type="image/avif"><img src="./Mega_Evolution_files/mega-evolution(1).png" alt="Set Symbol"></picture></div><button class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-transparent"></button></div><h1 class="font-bold text-black dark:text-white text-xl text-center mt-4">Mega Evolution Symbol</h1><p class="text-black dark:text-white text-sm"><strong><em>Click image to switch between symbol and logo</em></strong></p><p class="text-black dark:text-white mt-4 mb-2 text-left">The Mega Evolution expansion for the Pokémon TCG reintroduces Mega Evolution Pokémon EX cards, marked by a black-and-yellow EX symbol, which are worth three prize cards when defeated. It includes over 180 cards, sourced mainly from Japan’s Mega Brave and Mega Symphonia sets, plus reprinted Trainers. This set debuts full-art ultra rare Item, Tool, and Stadium cards, revives Mirror Holofoil variants, and features 10 Mega Evolution Pokémon ex, 22 illustration rares, and 10 special illustration rares.</p><p class="text-black dark:text-white mb-2 text-left"><strong>Series:</strong> Mega Evolution</p><p class="text-black dark:text-white mb-2 text-left"><strong>Released:</strong> September 2025</p><p class="text-black dark:text-white mb-2 text-left"><strong>Printed Total:</strong> 132</p><p class="text-black dark:text-white mb-2 text-left"><strong>Total:</strong> 188</p><p class="text-black dark:text-white mb-2 text-left"><strong>Pokémon Trading Card Game Online Code:</strong> MEG</p><p class="text-black dark:text-white mb-2 text-left"><strong>Equivalent Japanese Sets:</strong> <span><a class="text-sky-600 underline hover:no-underline dark:text-sky-400" href="https://pokesymbols.com/tcg/japanese-sets/mega-brave">Mega Brave</a>, </span><span><a class="text-sky-600 underline hover:no-underline dark:text-sky-400" href="https://pokesymbols.com/tcg/japanese-sets/mega-symphonia">Mega Symphonia</a></span></p><button class="mt-4 px-4 py-2 bg-sky-500 hover:bg-sky-600 dark:bg-sky-600 dark:hover:bg-sky-700 text-white rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring focus:ring-sky-300 dark:focus:ring-sky-400">Back</button></div></main><footer class="text-center p-4 border-t mt-8 border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700"><a class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700" href="https://pokesymbols.com/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a></footer><script src="./Mega_Evolution_files/webpack-a785c941f80c2152.js.download" async=""></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0]);self.__next_f.push([2,null])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"1:HL[\"/_next/static/media/e4af272ccee01ff0-s.p.woff2\",\"font\",{\"crossOrigin\":\"\",\"type\":\"font/woff2\"}]\n2:HL[\"/_next/static/css/f7538320a55d629a.css\",\"style\"]\n"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"3:I[5751,[],\"\"]\n6:I[9275,[],\"\"]\n7:I[1343,[],\"\"]\n8:I[4080,[\"56\",\"static/chunks/56-e66e0074fbab49ab.js\",\"123\",\"static/chunks/123-93ce515f5eb39144.js\",\"185\",\"static/chunks/app/layout-ef1dc6d4e9e8d826.js\"],\"\"]\n9:I[8026,[\"56\",\"static/chunks/56-e66e0074fbab49ab.js\",\"123\",\"static/chunks/123-93ce515f5eb39144.js\",\"185\",\"static/chunks/app/layout-ef1dc6d4e9e8d826.js\"],\"ThemeProvider\"]\na:I[8470,[\"56\",\"static/chunks/56-e66e0074fbab49ab.js\",\"123\",\"static/chunks/123-93ce515f5eb39144.js\",\"185\",\"static/chunks/app/layout-ef1dc6d4e9e8d826.js\"],\"default\"]\nb:I[5722,[\"489\",\"static/chunks/app/template-64542beda7e7a876.js\"],\"default\"]\nc:I[4404,[\"56\",\"static/chunks/56-e66e0074fbab49ab.js\",\"123\",\"static/chunks/123-93ce515f5eb39144.js\",\"185\",\"static/chunks/app/layout-ef1dc6d4e9e8d826.js\"],\"GoogleAnalytics\"]\ne:I[6130,[],\"\"]\nf:[]\n"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"0:[[[\"$\",\"link\",\"0\",{\"rel\":\"stylesheet\",\"href\":\"/_next/static/css/f7538320a55d629a.css\",\"precedence\":\"next\",\"crossOrigin\":\"$undefined\"}]],[\"$\",\"$L3\",null,{\"b